OL,5, A taxi driver's chance conversation    
OL,6, with a passenger led to him realising  
OL,7, she was about to become a fraud victim.
OL,9,FNayyer Iqbal Bhatti, 52, from Derby,   
OL,10,Fwas asked by his female passenger - who
OL,11,Fhe believes was about 80 - to drive to 
OL,12,Fa bank 15 miles (24km) away.           
OL,14,FShe said she had been told to do so by 
OL,15,Fa man who had rung her who she believed
OL,16,Fwas a fraud investigation officer.     
OL,18,FMr Bhatti alerted the bank - Barclays -
OL,19,Fwho told him it was a fraud. The bank  
OL,20,Fhas warned customers to be careful.    
